OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy at
OL,6,Ffirst with a few evening showers and a
OL,7,Fchance of a few thunderstorms, with
OL,8,Flightning, gusty winds and possible
OL,9,Fhail in the east. Rain then clearing
OL,10,Fto leave a dry, warm and humid night.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FVery hot and humid on Tuesday
OL,13,Fwith strong sunshine and light winds.
OL,14,FHigh humidity will intensify the heat
OL,15,Fmaking it feel uncomfortable.
